{"tid":1054211,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[投你心頭好]#周慧敏 龔嘉欣 何超蓮 衛詩雅 林穎彤 何依婷 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽第26輪投選專區","createTime":"2019-03-09T16:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T14:46:15.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a00c07748c640827d9a6d73c6481db19ad7a0093","tid":1054211,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:30am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n鄭宇澄 : 周慧敏<br />\n衛詩雅 : 何超蓮<br />\n林映蔚 : 鄺潔楹<br />\n勞嘉怡 : 林穎彤<br />\n蘇麗珊 : 駱文捷<br />\n車泳希 : 龔嘉欣<br />\n何雁詩 : 胡琳<br />\n何依婷 : 林凱恩<br />\n菊梓喬 : 陳華鑫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乙組第二十五輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/R77XaIR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FR77XaIR.png&h=ab0d6130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2IT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=59347059\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc62a7696643283ead94fb792b2b8738568bd3ea","tid":1054211,"uid":92376,"like":82,"dislike":8,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽第26輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-3-10 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bzPCRc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbzPCRc8.png&h=fe579f2c&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wVCWgva.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwVCWgva.png&h=72cf11c9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(3)鄭宇澄vs周慧敏(14)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" />natabcde vivianchowwaiman<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"65305ccf8947b2de5dcdfe8891e0c2d6061705e6","tid":1054211,"uid":92376,"like":62,"dislike":41,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-3-10 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/U7QbKTy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FU7QbKTy.png&h=628659bf&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rOaLdz7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrOaLdz7.png&h=22696728&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(4)衛詩雅vs何超蓮(5)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img s